description:
Good price! This 4 single bedrooms place open for everyone! You can use Room 3. Cozy and clean full size bed is suitable for one or two people. A private and modern full bathroom is only for you! Professional clean up for the public area. Personal passcode for every single room. There is a shared laundry in basement. I am sure you will like it because of perfect location and condition!

A private bedroom, shared kitchen shared living room and shared laundry in basement.

5 mins to Cermak-Chinatown Red Line Station;
5 mins to several bus station;
5 mins drive, 10 mins bus or 20 mins walk to McCormick Place;
10-15 mins to Downtown Chicago, Loop;
20 miles to O'Hare International Airport;
9 miles to Midway International Airport.

